This paper is likely to belong to the cs.MS (Mathematical Software) sub-category as it discusses the use of rule-based modelling for cellular signalling. It may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as the modelling approach can be used in these fields. Additionally, the paper may be relevant to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as these fields often use modelling techniques to understand complex systems.
